PS - There's a demostration RunNews file for !RiscBBS in the !News directory.
     Just copy it into your BBS.ANSI dir and {show} it at the appropriate time!
     Hows that for simple installation!


Bug in 1.00 - If (S)top is used, the news file isn't closed and therefore the program
crashes nastily. Bug fix by Keith Hall (#298 on Cryton). (03/05/92)